│[1m [0m[1mpatch_description       [0m[1m [0m│ This edit enhances the packing algorithm with three key improvements:                     │
│[1m                          [0m│                                                                                           │
│[1m                          [0m│ 1. **Diversified seeds**: Instead of just radial perturbations, we add grid-based         │
│[1m                          [0m│ initialization and corner-biased placement to explore different geometries.               │
│[1m                          [0m│                                                                                           │
│[1m                          [0m│ 2. **Faster radius computation**: Cache distance matrices and use vectorized operations   │
│[1m                          [0m│ where possible to speed up the LP solving, allowing more iterations.                      │
│[1m                          [0m│                                                                                           │
│[1m                          [0m│ 3. **Two-phase optimization**:                                                            │
│[1m                          [0m│    - Phase 1: Coarse optimization of centers with fewer LP calls (50 iterations)          │
│[1m                          [0m│    - Phase 2: Fine optimization with more intensive local search (150 iterations)         │
│[1m                          [0m│    - Phase 3: Final radius-focused refinement where centers are locked and we solve the   │
│[1m                          [0m│ LP precisely                                                                              │
│[1m                          [0m│                                                                                           │
│[1m                          [0m│ 4. **Better numerical conditioning**: Improve bounds enforcement and constraint matrix    │
│[1m                          [0m│ construction to help the LP solver converge better.                                       │
│[1m                          [0m│                                                                                           │
│[1m                          [0m│ This approach maintains the correctness of the LP formulation while increasing            │
│[1m                          [0m│ exploration breadth and depth, which should push us closer to 2.635.                      │
